description: Christmas is swinging into full gear as Johnny B and Dante Martin make it one holiday raw enough to remember. Watch as they push their device (and each other) to the limit, in this non-stop holiday fuck fest. Johnny might have been good all year, but he certainly shows just how naughty he can be, which is just how Dante likes it. They'll be spreading more than just Christmas cheer this December, that's for sure. Luckily, this is one holiday spectacle you're more than welcome to enjoy!
title: One Swinging Christmas
